/a>该歌曲出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mgmt">MGMT</a>的新专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mgmt-loss-of-life-review-lyrics-tracklist-3591340">Loss of Life</a> ”中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/christine-the-queens-shares-soulful-new-song-rentrer-chez-moi-a-metaphor-for-the-future-3751317">Christine &amp; The Queens 分享深情的新歌“rentrer chez moi”：“未来的隐喻”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
